imtixaan Haabiil: Habka tijaabada ee isku dhafka taxanaha aan dhammaadka lahayn
isu-keenid buuxda: Taxane aan dhammaad lahayn ayaa la sheegay inuu gabi ahaanba isu imanayo haddii wadarta qiimayaasha dhammaystiran ee isu-gudbinta ay dhammaato
ugu badnaan: Qiimaha ugu sarreeya ee shaqadu gaadho
ugu yar: Qiimaha ugu hooseeya ee shaqadu gaadho
qiimo buuxda: Qiimaha aan taban ee tirada dhabta ah iyada oo aan loo eegin calaamadeeda
taxane kale duwan: Taxane aan dhammaad lahayn oo erayadiisu ay u kala beddelanayaan togan iyo taban
imtixaan taxane beddela: Habka loo isticmaalo in lagu caddeeyo in taxanaha beddelka ah ee ereyada hoos u dhigaya qiimaha saxda ah uu yahay taxane isku dhafan
annulus: Walax giraan u qaabaysan, oo ah gobol ay ku xidhan yihiin laba goobood oo isku xidhan
antiderivative: Shaqo la kala saari karo oo ka-soo-saarkeedu la siman yahay shaqadii asalka ahayd
asymptote: Xariiq sida masaafada u dhaxaysa qalooca iyo xariiqdu u dhowdahay eber maadaama mid ama labadaba x ama y isku-dubaridku u janjeeraan inay dhammaadaan.
aagga qalooca hoostiisa: Dhexdhexaadinta u dhaxaysa qalooca y=f(x), dhidibka x, iyo xariiqyada toosan x=a iyo x=b, halka a iyo b ay yihiin xadka isdhexgalka
xeerka silsiladda: Kala-soocida shaqada isku-dhafka ah waa ka-soo-saar shaqada bannaanka ee lagu qiimeeyo waqtiyada shaqada gudaha
calculus kala duwan: Baro heerka isbeddelka tirada Isla'egta kala soocida waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu qeexo heerka isbeddelka shaqada
doorsoome madaxbannaan: Tiro lagu farsameeyay hawl ama isla'eg, inta badan matalaysa sababta xidhiidhka sabab-iyo-saamaynta
doorsoome ku tiirsan: Natiijada ama natiijadu waxay keentaa shaqo ama xidhiidh is beddela oo ku salaysan qiyamka tirooyin kale
domain: Waxay tilmaamaysaa dhammaan qiimayaasha suurtagalka ah ee loo isticmaali karo gelinta shaqada
kala duwan: Qaabka dhammaan wax-soo-saarka suurtogalka ah ee hawl-qabadku soo saari karto
xad: Fikrad qeexaysa waxa wax soo saarku qiimeeya shaqada ayaa ku soo dhawaada marka alaab-qeybiyeyaasha ay ku soo dhawaadaan qiimo gaar ah
asal ahaan: Fikrad cabbiraysa heerka degdega ah ee isbeddelka ama jiirada xariiqda tangent ee meel cayiman oo shaqo ah
xisaabinta aasaasiga ah: Kordhinta calculus taas oo ku lug leh helida antiderivative-ka shaqada kaas oo asalkiisa la bixiyay
line dhexgalka: Isku dhafka shaqada ee xariiqda qalooca
oogada midaysan: Isku-dubaridka agabyada kala duwan ee isku-dhafka dushooda
calculus kala duwanaansho leh: Kordhinta kalkulus ee hal doorsoome ilaa kalkulus oo leh hawlo doorsoomayaal badan leh
beerta vector: Bar meel bannaan oo leh baaxad iyo jihayn
calculus vector: Kordhinta calculus ee ka hadlaysa kala soocida iyo is dhexgalka goobta vector ee bannaanka Euclidean ee saddex-geesoodka ah
kartida vector: Goobta vector-ka taasoo keenta beer solenoidal ah iyada oo loo marayo hawlwadeenka curlka
